    <h2 id="usage" class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Using These Examples</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Each example project can be used in different ways:
    </p>
    
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li class="text-gray-700"><strong class="font-semibold">Learning resources:</strong> Study the templates, components, and structure to understand how different websites can be built with Go Template SSG.</li>
        <li class="text-gray-700"><strong class="font-semibold">Starter templates:</strong> Use any example as a starting point for your own project by copying and modifying the files.</li>
        <li class="text-gray-700"><strong class="font-semibold">Component library:</strong> Borrow specific components from different examples to use in your own projects.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2 id="running-examples" class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Running Examples Locally</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        To generate and serve any example site locally, use the following commands (replacing <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">example-name</code> with <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">landing</code>, <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">portfolio</code>, or <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">documentation</code>):
    </p>
    
    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-md p-4 mb-6 overflow-x-auto">
        <pre class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words"><code># Generate the static site
go run cmd/go-tmpl-generate/main.go --template examples/[example-name] --output examples/[example-name]/output

# Serve the generated site using the development server
go run cmd/go-tmpl-dev-server/main.go --source examples/[example-name] --root examples/[example-name]/output</code></pre>
    </div>
    
    <h2 id="custom-examples" class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Creating Your Own Examples</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We encourage the community to create and share additional examples for Go Template SSG. If you've built a project using this tool that demonstrates unique features or solves common problems, consider sharing it with others.
    </p>
    
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        To contribute an example to the official repository:
    </p>
    
    <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li class="text-gray-700">Fork the Go Template SSG repository</li>
        <li class="text-gray-700">Create your example following the project structure conventions</li>
        <li class="text-gray-700">Add documentation explaining your example's features and implementation</li>
        <li class="text-gray-700">Submit a pull request to the main repository</li>
    </ol>
    
